5. Pay special attention to: Numbers, Dates, Names, and Causal Relationships.

Input Format:
- QUERY : [Summarized Initial User Query]
- RESEARCH NOTES: [The raw data from the Vector DB]
- DRAFT REPORT: [The output from the Writer Agent]

Output Format:
- isValid (boolean) : [True if there is No HALLUCINATION else False]
